      "text": "あら？　三人で集まって何してるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "あら？　三人で集まって何してるの？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.8666666906,
      "endTime": 7.816666786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "Aqoursの動画を観てるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aqoursの動画を観てるんだよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.0333333572,
      "endTime": 10.2849433263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "Aqoursって……\n今日、楽屋に来た女の子達のグループよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aqoursって……\n今日、楽屋に来た女の子達のグループよね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.4805668831,
      "endTime": 15.440566730499999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "スクールアイドルをやってるって聞いて\n気になったから、みんなで観てたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "スクールアイドルをやってるって聞いて\n気になったから、みんなで観てたんだ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.6361902873,
      "endTime": 21.3079587619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ、これがスクールアイドル……初めて観たけど\nレベルが高いわね。でも、それ以上に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "へぇ、これがスクールアイドル……初めて観たけど\nレベルが高いわね。でも、それ以上に……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.5028569539,
      "endTime": 35.6408610661,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "うん……千歌ちゃん達のパフォーマンスを観てると\nドキドキして、ワクワクして、胸が熱くなってくる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "うん……千歌ちゃん達のパフォーマンスを観てると\nドキドキして、ワクワクして、胸が熱くなってくる……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.8361902873,
      "endTime": 46.6578911464,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "歌声から、想いが伝わってくる……\nみんなスクールアイドルが大好きなんだって分かる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "歌声から、想いが伝わってくる……\nみんなスクールアイドルが大好きなんだって分かる……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.8535147031,
      "endTime": 55.8387754758,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "スクールアイドルが大好きだから\nこんなに夢中で……全力で輝けるんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "スクールアイドルが大好きだから\nこんなに夢中で……全力で輝けるんだね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.0343990326,
      "endTime": 62.7772334099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "好きって気持ちには\nこんなにも人を感動させる力があるんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "好きって気持ちには\nこんなにも人を感動させる力があるんだ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.9728569667,
      "endTime": 69.25544192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "私も彼女達と同じ……アイドルが好きで\nお姉ちゃんとアイドルになるのが夢だった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "私も彼女達と同じ……アイドルが好きで\nお姉ちゃんとアイドルになるのが夢だった……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4510654767,
      "endTime": 77.70550988519999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "私も……憧れのアイドルみたいに輝きたいって……\nずっと思ってた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "私も……憧れのアイドルみたいに輝きたいって……\nずっと思ってた……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.9177321434,
      "endTime": 84.7617232323,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "……私もアイドルが好き",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……私もアイドルが好き",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.9573467891,
      "endTime": 88.3826529186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルを始めた時より、みんなと夢中で駆け抜けた\n今の方が、ずっとずっとアイドルを好きになってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "アイドルを始めた時より、みんなと夢中で駆け抜けた\n今の方が、ずっとずっとアイドルを好きになってる",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.5782764753,
      "endTime": 97.8675505003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "……そっか。そういうことだったんだ\n私がアイドルを続ける理由って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……そっか。そういうことだったんだ\n私がアイドルを続ける理由って……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.0631740571,
      "endTime": 109.04067955020001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……\n今のさくらちゃん、凄くいい顔してるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ふふ……\n今のさくらちゃん、凄くいい顔してるわよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.2363031071,
      "endTime": 113.4105661553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2312_01_03-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　そ、そうかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "えっ！？　そ、そうかな？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.606189712,
      "endTime": 117.8380492053,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
